    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you learn to master forbidden alchemical formulas - known as mutagens - that can temporarily alter your mental and physical abilities.</p><p>As a bonus action, you consume a mutagen, whose effects and side effects last until you finish a short or long rest unless otherwise specified. While one or more mutagens are affecting you, you can use an action to focus and flush all mutagens from your system, ending their effects and side effects.</p><p>Mutagens are designed for the specific biology of the character who concocted them, and your mutagens have no effect on other creatures. They are also unstable by nature, losing their potency over time and becoming inert if not used before you finish your next short or long rest.</p><div><h5>Mutagencraft Table</h5><table><thead><tr><th>Blood Hunter Level</th><th>Mutagen Created</th><th>Formulas Known</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3rd</td><td>1</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>2</td><td>5</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>2</td><td>6</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>3</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><td>18th</td><td>3</td><td>8</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
